{"about_the_game":"*Story<br />\r\nThe northeast of the kingdom is known as the Adventure World.<br />\r\nPeople build towns near dungeons which attract a bunch of adventurers to come here.<br />\r\nWith dreams, our heroine Alisa became one of these adventurers.<br />\r\nShe will write her own story with her sword.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n*Content<br />\r\nThe main story would be a guide for your adventure.<br />\r\nYou could also ignore it and do what you like.<br />\r\nPick up a random NPC on the street to be your partner or kidnap him/her for money.<br />\r\nMost monsters don't make you game over but morality does.<br />\r\nIf you keep doing bad things, your morality goes down and your career would come to an end soon.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n*Battle<br />\r\nAdventure World has a simple but various battle system.<br />\r\nYou have 3 battle styles .<br />\r\nDifferent partners support you in different ways.<br />\r\nThere's no particular solution about how to clear a dungeon.<br />\r\nAnd there isn't much penalty when you lose.<br />\r\nYou could keep trying tactics until you find a suitable one.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/465540/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1470455966","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/465540/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1470455966","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/465540/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1470455966","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/465540/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1470455966","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Trading Cards","id":29},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[1,5],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"*Story<br />\r\nThe northeast of the kingdom is known as the Adventure World.<br />\r\nPeople build towns near dungeons which attract a bunch of adventurers to come here.<b